<font color="#FF0000">OPEN CHALLENGE TO KALI TAL</font><br>
<tt>Thu May  1 23:28:18 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
My Dear Ms. Kali Tal:<br><br>
If you will only remove the &quot;I&quot; from your recent posting, you could save many sessions with your therapist.  Narcissism is the ultimate need to feed the &quot;I&quot;, to the dis-service of the majority, and you clearly stand guilty of such.<br><br>
If this site is so wrong, and we are so bad, because we operate without the &quot;strong hand of an editor such as you&quot; than I CHALLENGE all those that have written under your leadership, to open a NEW THREAD here, and engage this so called &quot;right wing&quot; veterans.  Call it the Ultimate Dialoge or what ever you want, but do it.  Come on Kali, let your people go! Let your writer, no, encourage &quot;your&quot; writers to take on Arthur, or DocDel, or Tom, or Chet, afterall, we are, and I count myself proudly as a &quot;we&quot; are just a small voice of individuals, we do not operate under the control of an editor such as you. <br><br>
Everyone wants to publish, and editors have writers by the throat, or balls, for eons.  I should know, having worked a MSS for the last 2 years and one of my best friends is a leading literary agent in NYC, so let your writers speak!!!.  Leave them alone, Kali, without your need for control and self ego fulfillment, and let us see what happens.  Right wing Vets? Damn me Kali, I thought they were all similar to Nazi's a few months ago, but then, I let let myself learn. Can you do the same?  I sure have learned something new, can you?<br><br>
doc spatz
